Whent he player comes to her with the fourth creature and tries to give it to her, she will start to take it, but her dialogue will spawn another character that comes running in with a string over his head saying the castle has been attacked. She will finish her dialogue and run to the castle, leaving the waterdhavian creature with the player.

She destroys herself as she enters the castle, and is replaced with Aribeth2
